nodes.text: The Piimi was a Strike-class medium cruiser that was used by the Rebel Alliance to defend the Sealion a prototype of the Missile Boat that was sent to the XQ4 Platform Enin'sd by the Mon Calamari Cruiser Link. That Strike-cruiser attacked the Imperial-class Star Destroyer Garrett but was destroyed in the battle.
